data.title: Emmanuel Faustino Obituary - Fort Smith, Arkansas
meta_keywords: Proudly Serving the Communities of Fort Smith
data.meta_description: Thank you for taking the time to visit our web site. A great deal of time and effort has gone into providing this service to our community and the families we serve. We are constantly enhancing and updating the information in this medium and hope that you find it helpful and convenient. If you have and questions or would like to share any suggestions on how we could improve this site, we value and encourage input.  We are here to continue to provide the highest standards for our community and to the families that we serve.
data.text: Proudly Serving the Families of Fort Smith, Crawford County, and Sebastian County
